successful_queries:
SELECT e.[EmployeeName],
f.[TotalHours] as ForecastedHours,
SUM(t.[TotalHours]) as ActualHours,
(SUM(t.[TotalHours]) - f.[TotalHours]) as Variance
FROM [Timesheet].[Employee] e
LEFT JOIN [Timesheet].[Forecast] f ON e.[EmployeeID] = f.[EmployeeID]
LEFT JOIN [Timesheet].[Timesheet] t ON e.[EmployeeID] = t.[EmployeeID]
GROUP BY e.[EmployeeName], f.[TotalHours]
ORDER BY Variance DESC
